OL,3,CMan attempted to drag police officer
OL,4,Ctowards canal after abuse warning
OL,6,FA man attempted to drag a plain-
OL,7,Fclothed police officer towards the
OL,8,Fcanal after being stopped for making
OL,9,Fan alleged homophobic remark.
OL,11,FPlain-clothed officers had overheard
OL,12,FMichael White, 40, making the comment
OL,13,Fwhile patrolling in Manchester's Gay
OL,14,FVillage in October 2022.
OL,16,FAfter being warned, White, of Millers
OL,17,FLane in Wigan, continued to be
OL,18,Fabusive, and officers attempted to
OL,19,Farrest him, Greater Manchester Police
OL,20,F(GMP) said.
