OL,3,CMan attempted to drag police officer
OL,4,Ctowards canal after abuse warning
OL,6,FDuring the arrest, he grabbed an
OL,7,Fofficer's arm, swung him around, and
OL,8,Fdragged him towards the canal before
OL,9,Ffellow officers were able to control
OL,10,Fand detain him.
OL,12,FWhite claimed he did not know the
OL,13,Fofficers were police and continued to
OL,14,Fdeny charges of assault of an
OL,15,Femergency worker.
OL,17,FBut he was found guilty at Manchester
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court on 1 September 2025
OL,19,Fand was ordered to pay #1,000 in court
OL,20,Fcosts and #100 in victim compensation.
