OL,6,FSuperintendent Nicola Williams, of
OL,7,FGMP's City of Manchester division,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Officers are committed to
OL,9,Fkeeping the public safe and our plain-
OL,10,Fclothed patrols are a vital part of
OL,11,Fensuring everyone can enjoy our city
OL,12,Fcentre's night life.
OL,14,F"White was not only heard to make
OL,15,Fhomophobic and discriminatory remarks
OL,16,Fin the Village; when approached by
OL,17,Fofficers he continued to be abusive
OL,18,Fbefore going to the extent of trying
OL,19,Fto drag an officer towards the canal.
